#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_packedbytearray.rst:123
msgid ""
"Returns a copy of the array's contents as :ref:`String <class_String>`. "
"Slower than :ref:`get_string_from_ascii "
"<class_PackedByteArray_method_get_string_from_ascii>` but supports UTF-8 "
"encoded data. Use this function if you are unsure about the source of the"
" data. For user input this function should always be preferred."
msgstr ""

